@node BUGSERRORS "Bugs, errors"

Bugs, errors etc.
-----------------

This program was written on A1200T with the following configuration:
    - Blizzard1240/40
    - 32 MB RAM
    - MerlinII/P96
    - Prelude/AHI
    - WD-850 MB HD
    - Iomega ZIP drive
    - Mitsumi 32xCDROM

using GCC 2.7.2.1 , GoldED and VinCEd-Shell.

However, the PPC option has not been tested, I still don`t own a PPC card.

@endnode
